	<p style="background-color:#FFFFFF;">The Salvation Army is launching the Hope House Campaign to respond to the urgent and growing need for emergency shelter and long-term stability in Madison County. With your help, we will build a dedicated facility designed to offer not just a place to stay, but a true path forward.</p>
