	<h2 style="background-color:#FFFFFF;">The Vision</h2>
	<div style="display:flex" className={styles.pvlRow}>
		<div style="flex:1" className={styles.pvlColumn}>
			<br>
			<br>
			<br>
			<br>
			<p>Hope House will be a 48-bed emergency shelter, offering:<br><br>Safe, dignified housing for individuals, families and couples<br>Private rooms with essential amenities<br>Case management and trauma-informed support<br>Job training and life skills programming<br>A launching point to permanent housing<br><br>Your support will help fund:<br><br>$6.5 million for the new Hope House facility<br>$500,000 for essential upgrades to our current Corps and 360 Center<br>$3 million to establish strategic reserves and endowment for sustainability<br></p>
		</div>
		<div style="flex:1" className={styles.pvlColumn}>
			<img width="100%" src="https://8hxvw8tw.media.zestyio.com/usc-mid-hope-house-boy.png" alt="placeholder">
